==Late 90's== The Waikato Cougars won the Super League Challenge Cup in 1997, defeating [[Canterbury rugby league team|Canterbury]] in the final. During this year they also defeated [[Auckland rugby league team|Auckland]] at [[Carlaw Park]] for the first time since 1943 and won the Rugby League Cup. They defended the Rugby League Cup in 1998.
==Bartercard Cup== {{Main|Waicoa Bay Stallions}} The Waikato region was represented in the [[Bartercard Cup]] competition by the [[Waicoa Bay Stallions]], a co-operative team involving players from Waikato, Coastline and Bay of Plenty federations.
